dicated their desire to participate in the Paris Games, but their Spanish clubs - Real Madrid where Mbappe, 25, is set to play next season and Atletico for 33-year-old Griezmann - have said they will not release them.\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.9028961834412029, \"rank\": 0.10441586494390682, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both players\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 199}, {\"ngram\": \"their desire\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 226}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 245, \"to\": 260}, {\"ngram\": \"Real Madrid\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"Mbappe\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 312}, {\"ngram\": \"next season\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World Cup-winning forward and France captain Mbappe will lead France at Euro 2024 which runs from June 14 to July 14 in Germany.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 487, \"end\": 493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.406954089167119e-18, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997917956758969, \"rank\": 0.00013481885010821243, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mbappe\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"Euro\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have to give a fairly realistic list, even if I know that it is virtual,\\\" said France Olympic football coach Thierry Henry, before adding that he was \\\"still hoping\\\" to be able to call upon Mbappe during the Olympic tournament.\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.406954089167119e-18, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thierry Henry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thierry_Henry\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fairly realistic list\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 594}, {\"ngram\": \"Mbappe\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 753}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic tournament\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everything is open for everyone, but we must give a list so that everyone can prepare.\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everything\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"a list\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But we are not closing the door to anyone.\\\"\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 915}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris Saint-Germain duo Warren Zaire-Emery and Bradley Barcola and Lyon forward Alexandre Lacazette were named in the preliminary list.\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warren_bioregion\", \"score\": 0.9999999672816108, \"rank\": 1.6036286656741944e-08, \"text\": \"Warren\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warren_bioregion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warren_bioregion\"}, {\"begin\": 986, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1523051989090837e-17, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Lyonnais\"}, {\"begin\": 999, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Lacazette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alexandre Lacazette\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Lacazette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alexandre_Lacazette\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paris Saint-Germain duo\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 942}, {\"ngram\": \"Bradley Barcola\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"the preliminary list\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a pre-list for preparation, it can evolve and, in my opinion, it will evolve,\\\" continued Henry, with the final deadline on July 3.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pre\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"list\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"my opinion\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"Henry\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1156}, {\"n